text: Phaeanthus ophthalmicus (synonym Polyalthia macropoda) is a species of plant in the family Annonaceae and tribe Miliuseae. It is a tree found in Peninsular Malaysia and Singapore.Kochummen, K.M. 1998. Polyalthia macropoda. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species.
